{"tid":1382080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"收集所有催淚彈過期、化學灼傷證據","createTime":"2019-07-29T11:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T02:45:37.000Z","uid":39752,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"27904ca93cedd1bf6f5e32b10c044ac63502ebdb","tid":1382080,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:32:51.000Z","msg":"有手足做完煙帽隊之後雙手起晒疑似化學灼傷嘅水泡[1]，另外連登亦有人影到催淚彈殼過咗有效日期[2]，我哋懷疑近日警方使用嘅催淚彈因為過期而對市民造成額外損害。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋想收集所有<br />\n1. 疑似夢遊後化學灼傷嘅證明<br />\n2. 過期嘅催淚彈殼</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n不論係你自己嘅相定係咁啱碌過 FB 連登望到，我哋都收。<br />\n請將圖片所有涉及敏感資訊嘅內容刪去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有 ac 嘅話</span></strong></span><br />\n可以直接回 post + upload 上嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無連登 ac 嘅 CD-ROM：</span></strong></span><br />\n請將 link 寄去我哋 google form<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/uKwsvbhzbBBky2mB8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FuKwsvbhzbBBky2mB8&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=bf554b6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/uKwsvbhzbBBky2mB8</a><br />\n如果需要 upload 圖或片，可以用 imgur 或 google drive（設定連結共用）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">收集完證據之後，我哋會將資料轉交催淚彈生產商以及聯合國，將件事推上國際。<br />\n（如果重有啲咩目的地啱使嘅話好歡迎大家提出意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n額外呼籲，如果有手足行街唔小心踢到過期催淚彈殼，建議立即用密封透明膠袋保存，需要時送去生產國即係美國領事館。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[1] <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1910695242353455/posts/2366617100094598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1910695242353455%2Fposts%2F2366617100094598&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=07d08609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1910695242353455/posts/2366617100094598</a><br />\n[2] <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1381844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1381844/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"dd48ee15ea70c8afb819bc225e473293656afe70","tid":1382080,"uid":39752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:33:54.000Z","msg":"唔記得講，執垃圾記得要抹乾淨先入袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2feee00bcaedb13c4e523640868d1fec26ed8f9a","tid":1382080,"uid":114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:36:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba71009bffa08aa7f25dd64a7d04173370e641b","tid":1382080,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdcf31ed57d23c59b70d8d44b2250ac1498779c","tid":1382080,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119cc2d1f9ab15440471ca4297c6bd4df7461833","tid":1382080,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8595f6061376150ec4939ecba02ba9bc0fbd48d8","tid":1382080,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbda6c7393d7dad1954cf0757df99c16bb57f690","tid":1382080,"uid":143827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite